<Function>om_encode(&thinsp;)</Function> and <Function>om_decode(&thinsp;)</Function>.
</Para>
</Sect1>
<Sect1 Id="DCEADG.REFSAP.div.5">
<Title>DS_C_ALGORITHM_IDENT</Title>
<Para>An instance of OM class
<Literal>DS_C_ALGORITHM_IDENT</Literal> records the encryption algorithm that an object
uses to digitally sign messages, together with the parameters of the
algorithm.
</Para>
<Para>An instance of this OM class has the OM attributes of its superclass,
<Symbol Role="Variable">OM_C_OBJECT</Symbol>,
in addition to
the OM attributes listed in Table 13-4.
</Para>
